title: Kaichou to Fukukaichou
sinopse:
1. President and Vice-President
   An irresponsible president with a crush on the vice-president. What happens ?! Read and see.

2. A Person Who Draws People
   Nashizuka-san is drawn in by the student council's president.

3. Rainy Days, Sunny Days
   The vice-president continues to explore her feelings and move closer to the president.

4. Daydream
